It was drunk by Paul.</div></p>
<p><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/s6/6-9-50.mp3">a</a>アップル　は　iPhone　を　作った。<br />
Apple made the iPhone<a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink61791873" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet61791873'))">Passivize! →</a>
