<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/s6/6-9-53.mp3">a</a>おんがく　は　こういちさん　に　きかれた。<br />
The music was listened to by Koichi</div></p>
<p><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/s6/6-9-54.mp3">a</a>マイケルさん　は　「アイ・ラブ・ユー」という　うた　を　うたいました。<br />
Michael sang the song known as &#8220;I love you.&#8221;<a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink153990882" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet153990882'))">Passivize! →</a>
<div class="ddet_div" id="ddet153990882"><script language="JavaScript" type="text/javascript">expand(document.getElementById('ddet153990882'));expand(document.getElementById('ddetlink153990882'))</script></p>
