The song known as &#8220;I love you&#8221; was sung by Michael.</div></p>
<p><a class="sm2_button" href="../../../audio/s6/6-9-56.mp3">a</a>お父さん　は　中田くん　を　見つけた。<br />
Father found Nakada.<a style="display:none;" id="ddetlink2064519492" href="javascript:expand(document.getElementById('ddet2064519492'))">Passivize! →</a>
